::GoldenEye::

She transformed into eagle mode, picked up Tails gently in her talons 
and flew off.  She flew to the cliffs where her nest was.  She set 
Tails down in the nest. "Now stay put. I don't want you falling 
down.  It's a loooonnnggg way down from here." She watched Tails to 
see what she would do.

> Tails crawled down a tree and leapt in front of
> Goldeneye.
> "You called?" She said with a smile. "Anyway, I'd like
> to learn more about the Maximals..and I would like to
> visit their base..." The squirrel then realised that
> Goldeneye couldn't exactly take her there, for fear of
> being shot.
> Tail sighed.
> 'Stupid war...' She muttered.
